# 👩‍💼 HR Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview  
This project presents an interactive **HR Analytics Dashboard** built using Power BI to analyze employee data, understand attrition trends, and support workforce decision-making.

---

## 🎯 Objectives  
- Analyze employee attrition patterns  
- Identify key factors influencing employee turnover  
- Understand department-wise and role-wise distribution  
- Provide insights for improving employee retention  

---

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies  
- Power BI  
- Excel  

---

## 📷 Dashboard Preview  

![HR Dashboard](dashboard1.png)

---

## 📈 Key Insights  
- Attrition rate is higher among employees with lower tenure  
- Certain departments show higher turnover rates  
- Salary and job role significantly impact attrition  
- Younger employees tend to leave more frequently  

---

## 🚀 Business Impact  
This dashboard helps HR teams to:
- Monitor employee attrition  
- Identify risk areas  
- Improve retention strategies  
- Make data-driven HR decisions  

